      "review": [
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Albert Varas"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2020-08-19",
          "reviewBody": "Tyler has been a fantastic financial leader for us during a tremendous growth stage for our non-profit. His help is invaluable in painting a clear picture of our finances & budgets so that we can continue to move the organization forward. It would have been difficult, if not impossible, to have tripled our budget in the past couple of years without Tyler's guidance and expertise.",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Blanca Mejia"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-06-20",
          "reviewBody": "It has been an enormous pleasure to work with Tyler and his team. We are a very small nonprofit in South Omaha, but with a big heart to serve our community. I know how you feel, and you struggle to make sure your numbers make sense so you can be well prepared for grant opportunities. Tyler and Luis have been a big piece in our journey. The Velu LLC team is a group of people who care about you. They don't see you only as another number. They take the time to ensure you understand and are doing well in your business. They work so hard to make sure you have all the tools you need to be successful in your nonprofit organization. I highly recommend them—Muchas gracias, Tyler and Luis, for everything you have done for Generation Diamond.",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Jade Rogers"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2020-08-10",
          "reviewBody": "Detail oriented, thorough, great service and a pleasure to work with! I have nothing but praise for Velu + Tyler!",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Michael Lewan"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-05-19",
          "reviewBody": "As a new nonprofit organization, we really appreciated the time and care Tyler gave us in filing our first ever 990 form. He turned what could have been a very complicated and laborious compliance obligation into easy to understand and manageable series of tasks.",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Gretchen Ellis"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-08-13",
          "reviewBody": "Tyler and his team are incredible to work with - efficient, thorough, and kind. Tyler's team completely remapped our chart of accounts and customized things to our nonprofit's needs. His team was efficient, helpful and understanding of the needs of nonprofits. We feel lucky and grateful for their support.",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Erin Goodwin"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-08-01",
          "reviewBody": "Our very small nonprofit that had become dysfunctional in our accounting. As we looked to grow, we realized the gaps in our processes were a real liability to the success of our mission. The backlog of unreconciled bank statements and improperly tracked donations became a huge source of stress. Thanks to Tyler and his intern Joselyn, we now have a proper accounting system set up, and we know how to maintain it. I am so grateful and delighted to move forward with financial transparency. Velu has been an absolute blessing. Thank you, Tyler, for sharing so much expertise and being so kind and supportive throughout the process!",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "McKenna Kiogima"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-09-29",
          "reviewBody": "Amazing assistance, communication, and people. Went above and beyond to help us set our quickbooks up for success, couldn't have had a better experience!",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Alex Goswami"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-06-23",
          "reviewBody": "Velu is organized, great tech stack, and very responsive. Not to mention experts in their field. Highly recommend!",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Dr. Erin Busch"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-08-20",
          "reviewBody": "Tyler was amazing to work with! He was extremely clear and consistent in all of our interactions, and was very patient with me as I navigated accounting software for the first time. I run a music nonprofit, and have zero training in accounting or bookkeeping, so I was starting from scratch. Along with his summer intern, they provided me with completed accounting books in QuickBooks Online & created helpful PDF tutorials that I have saved and can reference going forward. After I tried to input some sales & expenditures on my own and ran into some questions, I reached out to Tyler and he set up a Zoom for us right away. I am so grateful for his advice and time! I would highly recommend Tyler and his team to anyone who is looking for help getting started.",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Joe Nelson"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2020-12-05",
          "reviewBody": "Quality of work is exceptional and valued contributor on our board.",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Rachel Ziegler"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-01-05",
          "reviewBody": "Sharing a conversation with Tyler helped me grasp some key fundamental concepts so I can begin structuring my nonprofit appropriately and leave the organization in good hands. So thankful!",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Mike Pichik"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-09-30",
          "reviewBody": "Tyler Wilcox and the team at Velu have been phenomenal to work with. We are a new non-profit and they were great choice to navigate a very complex annual return!",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@id": "https://velu.us/services/grant-advisory-compliance-services#service"
